{"tid":637860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工黨軍營外示威促收地建屋","createTime":"2018-04-22T08:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T04:10:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6f742e9019bf1fd08a780d94094cc491fb10c407","tid":637860,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T08:14:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180422/20369106?_ga=2.15410230.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180422%2F20369106%3F_ga%3D2.15410230.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=aQe3t%2B%2BtQzHLQ0HOokJk7b%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=6234868f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180422%2F20369106%3F_ga%3D2.15410230.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=5ebb2295\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180422/20369106?_ga=2.15410230.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年04月22日 <br />\n<br />\n工黨軍營外示威促收地建屋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180422/large/22la4p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180422%2Flarge%2F22la4p4.jpg&h=6a17dec5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■工黨昨到九龍東軍營示威，要求政府檢討現行軍事用地的使用情況。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】由土地供應專責小組舉行為期5個月的公眾諮詢，將會於本周四（26日）展開，這場「土地大辯論」將會提供18個土地選項，但早前曾納入小組討論的「軍事用地」最終被剔走。工黨成員昨日去到解放軍駐港部隊位於九龍塘的九龍東軍營外示威，要求政府檢討現行軍事用地的使用情況。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃遠輝：房屋短缺或持續10年<br />\n<br />\n軍事用地曾被小組在會議中視為土地選項之一，最終政府指軍營並非置閒用地而剔除。工黨主席郭永健指出，現時香港有19幅軍事用地，共佔地2,700多公頃，「𠵱家有好多軍營都喺市區，駐軍人員只有1萬個左右，但無數嘅基層市民正係面對緊逼切嘅房屋問題」。<br />\n<br />\n郭又指，軍營被改建為房屋用途有先例，「𠵱家新蒲崗嘅采頤花園，當年都係彩虹軍營」，他希望政府可收回軍營發展，以紓緩現今的房屋問題。<br />\n<br />\n土地供應專責小組主席黃遠輝昨接受香港電台訪問時指出，公眾諮詢將會以設展覽區、公眾諮詢會、隨機抽樣電話訪問、會見政黨和專業團體等形式進行，他指房屋問題未能夠即時解決，「𠵱家嘅短缺一路要去到2028、2029先見到紓緩，呢個係我哋唔願見到嘅現實」，並指最後的建議報告會建基於公眾意見而撰寫，「小組冇前設，亦都相信政府唔會唔跟公眾意見」。郭永健就透露，於土地大辯論期間，工黨會繼續向政府表達訴求，「會去埋立法會層面，用一切嘅方法」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者李雨夢  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n【蘋果照相機】又係你呀？喬老爺！<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n議員倡港發揮自身制度優勢"},{"pid":"87f37dbfd1ab67fa22185b4dabe502fe36ab3b6a","tid":637860,"uid":82532,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T08:20:13.000Z","msg":"絕對應該啦, 九龍塘個軍營人影都唔多隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd8aabfc668aaed76c7a0ae38503e9a6b068e37","tid":637860,"uid":46275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:06:33.000Z","msg":"喺軍營門口日日播8964屠城片有無可能迫走班友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02450bdde6681f16ef0147761bca52a1b261f74","tid":637860,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:38:02.000Z","msg":"樓主泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/22/173801_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F22%2F173801_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=edbb9284&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9f343863d5ca4e5588626c7f9dd08022f952582","tid":637860,"uid":133519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:40:21.000Z","msg":"其實叫奧士本軍營"},{"pid":"a5af849a36dd8d9d27763ea05e9cd682212b0a52","tid":637860,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:42:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09905ea7f1cafc2978b9c5db18a73f563e491fa8","tid":637860,"uid":20227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:46:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d755cbd557e447936614c77c2243be7615a9c5b","tid":637860,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T10:38:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/b/b8/Camp_ArbeitMachtFrei.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fb%2Fb8%2FCamp_ArbeitMachtFrei.JPG&h=4c5c64f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8c10dcf6c0859d93ce45ea9f219acf93eec0b14","tid":637860,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T04:10:52.000Z","msg":"泛民工黨係港共走狗又一鐵證！<br />\n<br />\n想愚弄無知香港豬閪，根本丁屋用地對香港建屋土地影響極小，丁屋只局限在村界内，三尖8角而且已有其它村屋星佈其中，根本無乜用處。"}]}